songs.title: She Mine
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Love songs keep pumpin' on my radio
You split on Monday
Took your machine that kept me afloat
Now you're back, it's Tuesday

[Pre-Chorus]
I call it love insanity
I call it my reality

[Chorus]
She mine
Mine all mine
She mine
Mine all mine

[Verse 2]
Cool kids keep movin' as the car explodes
Roll around on Sunday
Dual-diagnosis is the way to go
Poppin' pills like candy

[Pre-Chorus]
I call it love insanity
I call it my reality

[Chorus]
She mine
Mine all mine
She mine
Mine all mine

[Bridge]
Wide array
Or how long this stays
Break the fray
Change

[Solo]

[Chorus]
She mine
Mine all mine
She mine
Mine all mine
